snippet.title: Seven of Heart
snippet.description:
This is a game made for the Godot wild Jam #33 (https://itch.io/jam/godot-wild-jam-32 ) where you need to collect 7 hearts to go to the next level.

You can play the game on:
https://jonasmv.itch.io/seven-of-heart
